9:
Oh, Inaho dear, would it kill you to 
smile?
...I know! Let's have a little chat!
12:
A little chat?! After what you have 
done to me?!
15:
Humor me, darling.
Let's talk about... Soushiro Kengyu!
I can make him yours.
17:
I can give you any man you desire—or 
lady! Goodness, you could ask for 
some unworldly yokai monster, I don't 
care! Treat yourself!
21:
Greed! Lust! Envy!
Once everything's merged together, 
ALL your darkest desires will come 
true!
28:
Yes! Our friend Orochi will gobble up 
every last crumb of light, and then!—In 
the infinite night, we shall share one 
infinite dream!
32:
Your words...
They are full of loneliness.
39:
Sharing your dreams with another is 
not such a difficult task. There are 
other ways—better ways!
43:
Silly girl, think bigger.
A puny world like this is HARDLY 
enough room for the kind of dream I'M 
talking about!
49:
I believe I told you to call me "Suizen," 
but no matter. This shall be our last 
meeting.
52:
Ooh, VERY scary, Izumi dear. Ahaha!
...You came here alone? Where's that 
fool Stella?
55:
Not here, not yet. By the time they 
arrive to deal with that serpent, you 
and I shall be long dead.
63:
Each of the five mountains around us 
governs one of the five elements—
which the diviners I've stationed are 
channeling here.
67:
My attendant is caring for your 
governess. Go—I'm sure she's worried 
about you.
71:
You! B-but why?!
What are you doing here?!
75:
Not happy I took away your nice, tasty 
fox, are you? I'm afraid you'll have to 
settle for me.
77:
Water douses fire, fire melts metal... If 
I channel the elements in destructive 
order, they'll destroy even you! Circle 
of Corrosion!
88:
What do you think you're doing?! 
You can't fight that thing alone!
91:
...I'm not alone. The seal on Orochi is 
holding back hundreds, THOUSANDS of 
spirits—which Orochi is feeding on for 
power. So long as they exist, Orochi is 
all but invincible.
94:
...Unless I consume them before it can! 
The Circle of Corrosion won't stop until 
it's destroyed every last spirit, mine 
included. Orochi will be powerless!
99:
I see... You've laid a terrible curse to 
gnaw away at Orochi's life, and intend 
pay for it with your own.
101:
Ahaha! You aren't as boring as 
I thought, Izumi! You're FAR more 
entertaining than the goody two-
shoes fox!
105:
Devour EVERYTHING, Orochi!
You've got eight perfectly good lives of 
your own! I'm sure you'll figure 
SOMETHING out!
109: I leave the rest in your hands...
119:
First you capture me, then you try to 
exorcise me, THEN you save me, and 
now this?! What are you DOING?!
120:
I cannot allow this! I WILL not allow 
this!
131:
Stay out of this!
Daemons, get rid of them!
135:
Stella! Inaho! Focus on Suizen!
...We'll take care of these!
